ZH: 我今天早上醒来的时候觉得很疲倦。
EN: When I woke up this morning, I felt very tired.

ZH: 我觉得这个问题很困难。
EN: I find this problem very difficult.

ZH: 我觉得你应该再多睡一会儿。
EN: I think you should sleep a little longer.

ZH: 你觉得这件衣服怎么样？
EN: What do you think of this clothing?

ZH: 我觉得这个决定是正确的。
EN: I think this decision is correct.

ZH: 你为什么觉得他有错？
EN: Why do you think he is wrong?

ZH: 他觉得这个城市很漂亮。
EN: He thinks this city is beautiful.

ZH: 我觉得明天会下雨。
EN: I think it will rain tomorrow.

ZH: 我觉得这部电影很有意思。
EN: I find this movie very interesting.

ZH: 我觉得他的回答不够详细。
EN: I think his answer is not detailed enough.

ZH: 他觉得学习汉语很困难。
EN: He finds learning Chinese very difficult.

ZH: 我觉得今天的天气非常好。
EN: I think today's weather is very nice.

ZH: 她觉得学习音乐很有趣。
EN: She finds learning music very interesting.

ZH: 我觉得这个想法很棒！
EN: I think this idea is great!

ZH: 我觉得这个菜的味道不错。
EN: I think this dish tastes good.

ZH: 你觉得怎样才能提高自己？
EN: What do you think can help improve yourself?

ZH: 我觉得你的提议很合理。
EN: I think your proposal is reasonable.

ZH: 爸爸觉得这里不适合生活。
EN: Dad thinks this place is not suitable for living.

ZH: 我觉得这个职位对我来说很适合。
EN: I think this position is very suitable for me.

ZH: 妈妈觉得这个饭馆很不错。
EN: Mom thinks this restaurant is very good.
